History
========================================

1.0.17 (2017-05-24)
----------------------------------------

* Fix word_sent method
* Enhance performance
* Add word_sent package

1.0.9 (2017-03-07)
----------------------------------------

* Add Corpus class
* Add Transformer classes
* Integrated with dictionary of Ho Ngoc Duc
* Add travis-CI
* Auto build with PyPI

1.0.0 (2017-03-01)
----------------------------------------

* First release on PyPI.
* First release on Readthedocs


